"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1929536-Novak-Djokovic-Rafael-Nadal-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Novak Djokovichas shed light on his relationship withRafael Nadalafterbeating the Spaniard in the second round of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal has arguably been Djokovic's biggest rival and Tuesday's match was their 60th meeting.\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999940762336, \"rank\": 5.923830076776504e-09, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although their careers have been so intertwined, the Serb later confessed that he had not been able to \\\"connect\\\" with the 38-year-old.\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think there is no brotherhood really.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's more rivalry, colleagues, respecting each other, appreciating each other's careers and what we have achieved and brought to the sport,\\\" Djokovic said after beating Nadal 6-1 6-4.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999940762336, \"rank\": 5.923830076776504e-09, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Explaining why they could not be friends, the 24-time Grand Slam champion continued: \\\"It's tough to be close, honestly.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[We are] greatest rivals and you do not want to maybe give insights into your life or the way you feel and stuff because that can maybe expose you and stuff.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I guess that's one of the reasons why we did not connect so close and I do not think at that level you can really connect so close to anybody really.\\\"\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Long-standing WTA event scrapped and worries raised that more will follow  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    But Djokovic is leaving the door open for a friendship when they have both retired.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999940762336, \"rank\": 5.923830076776504e-09, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"But who knows?\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When the career ends for both of us, it's a long life hopefully for both of us, we are both family people and hopefully we can address the different side of the relationship and reflect on things that we went through together, that we lived together, the special moments, in a different way.\\\"\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, the world No.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2 wants to prolong his professional relationship with Nadal by facing off at least one more time before the ends of their respective careers.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999911797204, \"rank\": 8.820284165986992e-09, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course it can be but we do not know that,\\\" he replied when asked whether his Olympics win over Nadal could have been their last match.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1930, \"end\": 1935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999911797204, \"rank\": 8.820284165986992e-09, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It really depends on many different factors, it depends on whether both of us will keep going and whether we are going to participate in the same tournaments or not.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we both want to play in the Grand Slams and the biggest tournaments.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Jack Draper 'not meeting other athletes' at Olympics after making costly mistake  Do not miss:Dan Evans shows true colours with Andy Murray comments after Emma Raducanu snub  Do not miss:Caroline Wozniacki brutally mocks Olympics 2024 opponent mid-point in Paris  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9971717202711319, \"rank\": 0.0028363015638489994, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6645937534964324e-43, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}, {\"begin\": 2415, \"end\": 2433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Wozniacki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Wozniacki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Wozniacki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Wozniacki\"}, {\"begin\": 2485, \"end\": 2490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999920139544, \"rank\": 7.986004947671257e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    \\\"I do not know, we will probably be very selective, I can speak on my behalf, I will be very selective with the tournaments I play.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just hope for the sake of our rivalry and the sport in general that we will get to face each other once or maybe a few times, different surfaces in different parts of the world because I feel like it can only benefit the sport.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But as I said, I do not know how he feels in his body, what his plans are, let us hope we can play some more.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope we are going to play more because every match is like a present, to us and to the sport itself.\\\"\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3454, \"end\": 3467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.252904433686102e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3503, \"end\": 3516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.252904433686102e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"